Class BaseTwoWayConverter<From,To>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.broadcasters.Multicaster
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.repeaters.BaseRepeater
com.telenav.kivakit.conversion.BaseConverter<From,To>
com.telenav.kivakit.conversion.BaseTwoWayConverter<From,To>
Type Parameters:
From - The type to convert from
To - The type to convert to
All Implemented Interfaces:
Converter<From,To>, TwoWayConverter<From,To>, Broadcaster, Listener, MessageTransceiver, Repeater, Transceiver, Receiver, Transmitter, Nameable, NamedObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
AttachmentConverter, BodyConverter
public abstract class BaseTwoWayConverter<From,To> extends BaseConverter<From,To> implements TwoWayConverter<From,To>
Base class for implementing two-way converters.

Adds to BaseConverter an implementation of unconvert(Object) that checks for null, catches exceptions and called onUnconvert(Object).

Conversions

  • Converter.convert(Object) - Called to convert from => to
  • unconvert(Object) - Called to convert to => from

Implementing Converters

  • BaseConverter.onConvert(Object) - Called to convert from => to
  • onUnconvert(Object) - Called to convert to => from

Missing Values

  • nullValue()
